parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description: The end of the time range when event traces are queried. Unit: milliseconds.

parameters.name: EventBusName
parameters.description: The name of the event bus.

parameters.name: EventSource
parameters.description: The name of the event source.

parameters.name: Limit
parameters.description: The maximum number of entries to be returned in a call. You can use this parameter and NextToken to implement paging. Up to 100 entries can be returned in a call.

parameters.name: MatchedRule
parameters.description: The name of the event rule that is matched.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: If you configure Limit and excess return values exist, this parameter is returned.

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: The beginning of the time range to query event traces. Unit: milliseconds.
